4Geeks Academy offers a bootcamp to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer, designed for beginners with no previous knowledge. Over 16 weeks, students learn Python, SQL, and key statistics, focusing on building predictive models and applying algorithms like decision trees and k-nearest neighbors. The program includes 3 classes per week and accommodates a maximum of 12 students per class. Notable instructors with expertise in AI and machine learning lead the course. Participants receive industry-recognized certificates upon completion. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop